# Using GHCJS - The Haskell to JavaScript Compiler

### Installing packages

    cabal install --ghcjs <package-name>


### Running in node

Compile and run

~~~
ghcjs <myfile>.hs
node <myfile>.jsexe/all
~~~

### Running in the browser

Compile and run

~~~
ghcjs <myfile>.hs
~~~

Point browser to 

~~~
../<myfile>.jsexe/index.html
~~~


### Running interactive in the Browser

* Start interactive ghcjs session

~~~
ghcjs --interactive
~~~    

* Connect from the browser to ghcjs

~~~
http://localhost:6400
~~~